# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Notes:
# • Keep flame/exports out of Git — they’re reproducible via scripts/generate_flame.py
# • Use .keep files in empty dirs you want tracked (already whitelisted above).
# • Never commit tokens: PATs, API keys, or URLs containing credentials.
# • If you previously embedded a token in a remote URL, switch back to clean HTTPS:
#   https://github.com/<owner>/<repo>.git (Working Copy caches the token in Keychain).
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────